Overview

What Is CO2 Renew?

CO2 Renew is a topical CO2 therapy paste that triggers the body's natural oxygen delivery response. When applied to the skin, it activates the Bohr Effect—increasing circulation, oxygenation, and visible skin vitality. It works with the body, not against it. No devices. No complexity.

What You'll See

Core Benefits

  • Instantly brightens and revitalizes skin
  • Improves circulation and oxygenation
  • Supports smoother, more even tone
  • Leaves skin visibly refreshed post-treatment
  • Enhances the overall facial experience
The Science

How It Works

CO2 is applied to the skin. The body responds by increasing oxygen delivery to the treated area. This creates a visible revitalization effect—brighter, more alive skin.

→

Protocol

How to Use in a Facial

1
Apply

Apply approximately 2 mL of CO2 Renew paste evenly across the treatment area on clean skin.

2
Activate

Allow the paste to activate on contact with the skin. The body's natural oxygen response begins immediately.

3
Observe

Watch for subtle circulation increase and brightening. Remove after activation period and continue facial as normal.

~2 mL per service. A thin, even layer is all you need. More product does not mean more effect—consistency of application matters most.
